SAPO,is,a,Portuguese,Internet,service,provider,whose,main,web,site,acts,as,a,web,portal,featuring,a,directory,of,Portuguese,sites,SAPO,Services,provides,a,large,suite,of,web,services,and,applications,to,developers,worldwide,The,Advertising,API,allows,users,to,manage,campaigns,on,Sapo,Adverts,without,accessing,the,platform,The,API,provides,methods,for,creating,and,managing,campaigns,as,well,as,viewing,reports,The,API,uses,RESTful,calls,and,responses,are,formatted,in,JSON